name: Adventure Ahoy; A Slight Case Of Weather; Castaway Island; A Rip-Snortin' Rescue; Westward Ho-Ho-Ho!; Canyon Capers; Make Way For Hollywood; Paging Mr. Rockmore!

description: Professor Pither has a new source of power. Sabrina (temporarily upgraded by Head Witch Della to a Teen Witch Two) tracks him and the Time Taxi back into the ancient past to remove it.
The Explorers contend with Dr. Zarkon, a mad geneticist who created monstrosities in his lab at Lodge Industries and was fired when he was discovered. Now he wants revenge.
name: The World of Archie
